{"tid":2507514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺193有大頭症（有禮貌運動）","createTime":"2021-04-28T05:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T05:38:03.000Z","uid":317635,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e137fad4725fef145d6efc243ae758027d7991","tid":2507514,"uid":317635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"我之前言辭過於粗俗<br />\n為響應連登有禮貌運動<br />\n現已深切反省自身<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcMcGf8yEAu38Z9Ts2eB9WXebMTRBDa9cUdPPUAE2kQhs?filename=U3q3sWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3q3sWW.png&h=6bf190aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人認為咁樣唔算係講嘢直率<br />\n而係一種自滿 囂張嘅表現<br />\n我並未曾見過有藝人會咁樣講<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你無唱跳實力上選秀<br />\n就會有批評呢個係好正常嘅事<br />\n我認為唔應該因為最近有少少話題度就衝出黎抨擊人地<br />\n唔係話你唔評擊得<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係現時難道你係明星了嗎？<br />\n我希望你深切反省<br />\n身為有一點知名度的人 開全名公審人是不好的事<br />\nError唔係做乜都得 <br />\n唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝大家睇到呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cd782f12aa7ea96fe084041a615e207e59782d","tid":2507514,"uid":317635,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"同193講返句唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15fcb25e0244bfa8f300c89377e3de6694fb0aa","tid":2507514,"uid":317635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"同大家講返句唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aac61838f522b3c44c410dc104bcfaf80cfd76","tid":2507514,"uid":195743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩<br />\n支持193"},{"pid":"03470b4ffd20ca73e71f1f9f27fd62e8dbfad6be","tid":2507514,"uid":156130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB